comments.body:
We have been experiencing this issue ever since I stood up a new 4.2.1 environment with VPC. It takes 2-3 minutes to create any instance in our cloud. We are seeing the following error messages repeatedly on the NC nodes until the instance is in the running state:
{noformat}
2016-08-25 07:23:45 DEBUG 000027526 instance_network_gate    | [i-f57a6c2b] version (c05be5c5) and applied version (50cc9b3b) do not match (yet), waiting
{noformat}
Even after an upgrade to 4.2.2 we are still experiencing this issue. I will continue to investigate why Midonet is causing a delay here.
